{"type":"article_comment","id":115338,"parentType":"article","parentId":8544,"uid":9304,"contents":"伊朗日前因油價上漲引爆抗议，迅速延烧到全國。這次抗議有幾個特點：<br>\n一，僅因油價上漲就引爆一場革命，說明獨裁者已極為不得人心；<br>\n二，全國各地公路被堵，交通基本癱瘓；<br>\n三，各地民眾憤怒焚燒銀行、加油站等國資企業；<br>\n四，直接針對警察進行攻擊，大量焚燒警車。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJh2cwhVUAAn7Lk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJh2cwhVUAAn7Lk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJh2cwhVUAAn7Lk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJh2cwiVUAAoVHF?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJh2cwiVUAAoVHF?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJh2cwiVUAAoVHF?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJg_2MxXkAE2lFD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJg_2MxXkAE2lFD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EJg_2MxXkAE2lFD?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-11-18","agreeCount":17,"discussionCount":0}